race.comment: KANTISHNA (3) at her top now and doesn't have to improve much to win this. Nailed late from the wide gate when second over 900m at Muswellbrook in BM66 class. Will take catching in this company. QUICK ONYX (9) drops in weight and saves her best for this track and trip. Just under a month between runs when a dismal ninth over 1100m at Dubbo. Assess on her good second two-back at this course. DESIROUS (7) is yet to fill a placing in two runs back. Since fitted with a trial placing over 1000m at Bathurst after fading in the run when seventh over 900m at Newcastle. Has never been out of the placings at the third run in and can find peak form this time. NAVY STEEL (1) returns from a layoff of five months. Scored over 1000m at Wellington at the start of last prep. Worth plenty of thought, despite shouldering the 62.5kg.
